content.description: Face climb for 3 bolts, then traverse right & up to a short crack that ends. Clip 1 more bolt, then follow the right leaning crack to " Rize of the fenix" anchor
content.protection:
4 bolts & gear to 1.5 in.

Shares anchor with "Rize of the fenix", Mussy hooks
content.location:
Start just left of the big block that leans against the cliff,

5 ft. right of " Felix Char "

Go left after cliping 1st bolt towards big block leaning against cliff, DON'T GO UP CRACK! Then go straight up

angling back left slightly at the end for the last bolt & the anchor

Climb it until it ends at the horizontal finger crack, move left

around the bulge then up the face past 2 bolts

finally, clip the last 2 bolts of & finish on " Kielbasa ".

put a long sling on your 1st piece in the traverse to cut

down on rope- drag
